name: Dystopia
description:
We dream of having a beautiful civilization, an advanced civilization without oppression.

We dream of building a high-tech city like Cyberpunk City, with all the ease of access in the future.

But what do we get?  Falsehood.
The progress we desire is the destruction of all aspects of life.
The high technology we have makes humans die slowly.
Our dreams of a peaceful life in the future contradict what we do.

The direction of life that we are living is the road to destruction.
If capitalism and industrialism still hold the stick of virtue.
